# Sports Booking System

## Purpose
A full-stack sports facility booking platform where users can search, filter, and book sports facilities.

## Live URL
https://your-live-site.vercel.app

## Features
- User authentication (JWT)
- Facility search system
- Sport type filtering
- Booking system
- Protected routes
- Responsive design
- MongoDB integration

## NPM Packages Used

### Client
- next
- react
- tailwindcss
- axios
- react-hot-toast

### Server
- express
- mongodb
- cors
- jsonwebtoken
- cookie-parser
- dotenv